casebody.data:
Tuesday, October 25, 1994

MOTION DOCKET

94-2216. Marsala v. Marsala.

Cuyahoga County, No. 67301. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal and a claimed appeal of right. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion to stay enforcement of judgment,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion to stay enforcement of judgment be, and the same is hereby, denied, effective October 24, 1994.

Resnick, F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., dissent.
